# ============================================================
# SECURITY OVERVIEW
# ============================================================

status: canonical-draft
phase: design-only

security_objectives:
  - 最小共有
  - 高秘匿情報の誤露出防止
  - export 派生物の取り扱い分離
  - 権限変更の追跡可能性
  - 端末利用を前提にした保護

control_areas:
  - app access control
  - case visibility control
  - document confidentiality control
  - share audit control
  - export handling control

core_controls:
  - app lock
  - biometric unlock
  - auto lock
  - share audit
  - high confidentiality protection
